; DNS zone example for research.2884.kr
; Apply on the authoritative DNS server for 2884.kr.
; Current authoritative NS observed: ns.2884.kr, ns1.2884.kr
;
; Public DNS should point to the public reverse-proxy IP.
; 2884.kr currently resolves to 112.155.36.24, so research can normally use the same public proxy IP.

research.2884.kr. 3600 IN A 112.155.36.24

; Optional split-horizon/LAN DNS only:
; research.2884.kr. 3600 IN A 192.168.0.200
; or, if clients directly reach the Linux PC on LAN:
; research.2884.kr. 3600 IN A 192.168.0.199
